<div class="band-hero page-width">
	<h1>Omni Code is a Visual Studio extension that brings a full-featured TIScript editor and enhancements for writing your HTML based code for Sciter technology</h1>
	<div class="row">
		<div class="col-md-5 col-sm-12 col-xs-12">
			<ul>
				<li>-TIScript editor works for <b>.tis</b> files and for code inside <b>@("<script />")</b> tags in HTML</li>
				<li>-Full-featured <b>CSS editor</b> for Sciter specific syntax</li>
				<li>-Complete <b>Intellisense</b> support: auto-complete, signature help, quick-info</li>
				<li>-TIScript type inference by code-convetions: <a href="~/OmniCode/Convention">see the table</a></li>
				<li>-Snippets (<a href="https://github.com/midi-sciter/OmniCode-Snippets">requires installation</a>)</li>
				<li>-Many more features, <a href="https://docs.google.com/presentation/d/132GgHy3w7S_cP_YRIV5RJFioMSSOVNpEN1l_Zq5BFCU/edit?usp=sharing">see slides</a></li>
			</ul>
		</div>
		<div class="col-md-7 col-sm-12 col-xs-12">
			<img src="~/Content/img/omnicode_hero.png" class="img-screen"/>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>

<div class="band-screens">
