				<div class="legend">Exclusive editor for Sciter specific <b>CSS syntax/attributes map</b> (<a href="https://docs.google.com/presentation/d/132GgHy3w7S_cP_YRIV5RJFioMSSOVNpEN1l_Zq5BFCU/edit#slide=id.g1210e835cd_0_0">read more</a>)</div>
