			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-md-6">
				<b>Well-known IDE</b><br />
				<img src="~/Content/img/omnicode/omnicode_screen_native.png" />
				<div class="legend">Use the same IDE for writting C#/C++/D <b>native code</b> and your <b>HTML/CSS/TIScript</b> content</div>
			</div>
			<div class="col-md-6">
				<b>Integrated Sciter documentation</b><br />
				<img src="~/Content/img/omnicode/omnicode_screen_docs.png" />
				<div class="legend">Easily navigate the Sciter docs inside VS through a separate tool window</div>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-md-6">
				<b>TIScript API database</b>
				<img src="~/Content/img/omnicode/omnicode_screen3.png" />
				<div class="legend">Autocompletion and signature help for the entire TIScript API; for methods, constants and properties, <b>press F12 in the identifier</b> to show-up its documentation</div>
				
			</div>
			<div class="col-md-6">
				<b>Fundamental coding features</b>
				<img src="~/Content/img/omnicode/omnicode_screen4.png" />
				<div class="legend">Outlining for blocks of classes, functions and closures; smart-indent, brace completion, comment/uncomment selection, and much more</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>

